{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "第三回\"千蛇怪剑\"，燕十三与乌鸦在树林外喝酒，见青衣小孩系红丝带标记禁地。太行大刀十一骑冲入树林欲寻衅，皆被琴声主人击飞。翠衫少妇携幼童进入树林后安然离去。随后夏侯星与妻子薛可人出现，遣青衣小孩向燕十三索要舌头和眼睛。燕十三与乌鸦戏弄小孩后，薛可人自报家门称赞丈夫剑法高超。乌鸦出言嘲讽，夏侯星怒而出手，以千蛇剑与乌鸦交锋。薛可人趁乱逃走，夏侯星追去。最后神秘少年小讨厌现身，与燕十三对话，透露燕十三名字由来，并以绿丝带标示地盘，暗示其与翠衫少妇的关系。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "看来我们还是换个地方去喝酒的好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "这地方不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "很好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "既然很好，为什么要换？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "因为这个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "这意思就是说，这地方暂时已成了禁地，谁都不能再进去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是哪里的规矩？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "这些人是不是太行来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "太行大刀果然有胆子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你看他们是干什么来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "是来送死的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "他们果然是来送死的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "想来送死的好像还不止他们这几个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "还有我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "现在还轮不到你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "青衣小孩",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你们是不是已经来了很久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "青衣小孩",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "刚才的事，你们都看见了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "青衣小孩",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你知道咱们是从哪里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "火焰山，红云谷，夏侯山庄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "青衣小孩",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你知道的事看来倒还真不少。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "你叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "青衣小孩",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你不必问我的名字，我也不是跟你们攀交情来的！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "你是干什么来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "青衣小孩",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "我们公子想要向你们借三样东西，每个人三样！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "哪三样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "青衣小孩",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "一根舌头，两只眼睛。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "没关系，我小时就常常被大人这样抛上去。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "这么样可以练胆子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "你要来拿的东西，没有拿走，回去怎么交代？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "青衣小孩",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "我可以教你个法子。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "你们的公子，是不是夏侯公子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "是不是他要你来拿的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "那么你就可以回去问他，既然是他想要这三样东西，他为什么不自己来拿？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我叫薛可人，站在那边的，就是我丈夫夏侯星。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "原来是红云谷的少庄主。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "两位既然听说过他的名字，也该知道他是个什么样的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "他是个天才，不但文武双全，剑法之高，更少有人能比得上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "像他这么样一个人，两位当然是不会跟他动手的！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "因为他不但家世显赫，自己又那么了不起，两位跟他动手，岂非鸡蛋碰石头，所以我劝两位还是……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "还是乖乖的割下舌头，剜出眼睛来送给他？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "那样子虽然有点不方便，至少总比送掉性命的好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "你这位文武双全的公子爷是不是哑巴？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "speaker_name": "薛可人",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "当然不是！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xue_ke_ren",
      "text": "那么这些话他为什么不自己来说？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算他是个哑巴，屁眼总有的，这些屁他为什么不自己来放？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "他既然不过来，我们为什么不能过去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "能！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "是你去？还是我去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "据说他的藕断丝连，满天星雨千蛇剑，不但是把好剑，而且是把怪剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "他若死了，他的剑归谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "归你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "你不想要那把剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "想！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "你为什么不抢着出手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "因为我懒得跟这种兔崽子交手，我一看他就讨厌。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "我要找的却是你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "text": "那就快拔你的剑！",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一战应该让我来，这柄剑我也想要。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "这一战你们就算不分胜负，现在由我来！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "这是谁下的手？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "青衣小孩",
      "listener": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "text": "是……夫人！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "text": "夫人呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_xiao_hai",
      "speaker_name": "青衣小孩",
      "listener": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "text": "夫人已跑了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "我叫小讨厌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "你明明一点都不讨厌，为什么要叫小讨厌？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "你明明是个人，为什么要叫乌鸦？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "你知道他叫乌鸦？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "废话。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我不但知道他叫乌鸦，还知道你叫燕十三，因为从前有个人叫燕七，又有个人叫燕五，你自己觉得比他们两个人加起来还要强一点，所以你就叫燕十三。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "其实我根本不知道你是老几，这件事我只不过是听我姐姐说的！",
      "tone": "调皮",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "你姐姐有没有名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "当然有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "她叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你是不是哑巴？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你有没有腿？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你既然有腿，又不是哑巴，为什么不自己问她去？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "因为我也不是瞎子，我还看得见。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "看得见什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "这个结既然是你打的，你当然应该明白它的意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "这意思就是说，这地盘已是我们的，不是哑巴的进去也会变成哑巴，有腿的进去也会变成没有腿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 409
    }
